BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2005/US/04/10/klm.flight/index.html"&gt;U.S. bars KLM flight entry into airspace&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 10,2005

