BULLET::::- Michael Kranish. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.boston.com/news/nation/washington/articles/2005/06/07/yale_grades_portray_kerry_as_a_lackluster_student/"&gt;Yale grades portray Kerry as a lackluster student&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABoston%20Globe"&gt;Boston Globe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 7, 2005
BULLET::::- Stephen Braun, Times Staff Writer. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/nation/la-na-kerry8jun08%2C0%2C3048402.story%3Fcoll%3Dla-home-nation"&gt;Kerry Makes His Military, Medical File Available&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AL.A.%20Times"&gt;L.A. Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 8, 2005 }
