BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.usatoday.com/news/world/2005-06-07-world-military_x.htm%3FPOE%3DNEWISVA"&gt;Report: World military spending tops $1T in 2004&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUSA%20Today"&gt;USA Today&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 7, 2005
