<ul>
BULLET::::- Sarah Kennedy. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.edmontonsun.com/News/Alberta/2005/06/08/1076719-sun.html"&gt;It’s soggy down south&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASun%20Media"&gt;Sun Media&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 8, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//calgary.cbc.ca/regional/servlet/View%3Ffilename%3Dca-flooding-rivers20050607"&gt;Riversrise, overflows banks&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACBC"&gt;CBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 7, 2005
BULLET::::- Rochelle Squires. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.canoe.ca/NewsStand/WinnipegSun/News/2005/06/08/1076379-sun.html"&gt;Cryin’in the rain&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASun%20Media"&gt;Sun Media&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 8, 2005
