BULLET::::- &lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATidningarnas%20Telegrambyr%C3%A5"&gt;TT&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.dn.se/DNet/jsp/polopoly.jsp%3Fd%3D147%26amp%3Ba%3D426292"&gt;Antipiratbyråns övervakning olaglig&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ADagens%20Nyheters%20n%C3%A4tupplaga"&gt;Dagens Nyheters nätupplaga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 10, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//piratbyran.org/index.php%3Fview%3Dforum%26amp%3Ba%3Dthread%26amp%3Bid%3D30273"&gt;Seger över Antipiratbyråns registrering!&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APiratbyr%C3%A5n"&gt;Piratbyrån&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 10, 2005
