BULLET::::- Stephen Labaton. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/06/10/arts/television/10pbs.html"&gt;Panel Would Cut Public Broadcasting Aid&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANY%20Times"&gt;NY Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 10, 2005
BULLET::::- David Folkenflik. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php%3FstoryId%3D4698411"&gt;Congress Looks to Cut Funding for Public Broadcasting&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAll%20Things%20Considered"&gt;All Things Considered&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 10, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi%3Ffile%3D/chronicle/archive/2005/06/10/MNG8SD6JON1.DTL"&gt;House panel OKs big cuts in public broadcast funding&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASFGate.com"&gt;SFGate.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 11, 2005
