BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/4079174.stm"&gt;Glazer 'plans ticket price rises'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News"&gt;BBC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 10, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0%2C%2C2-1648571%2C00.html"&gt;Ticket prices rise, transfer cash is limited and income forced up&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Times"&gt;The Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 10, 2005

