BULLET::::- David A. Lieb. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.kansascity.com/mld/kansascity/news/local/11838086.htm"&gt;Judge orders Planned Parenthood to pay back state family planning money ♡❤♡- registration required♡❤♡&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AKansas%20City%20Star"&gt;Kansas City Star&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 7, 2005
