BULLET::::- Michael Smith and Tim Hepher. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.reuters.com/newsArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DbusinessNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D8774657"&gt;Qatar in $15 bln boost for Airbus, Boeing&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 13, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/businesstechnology/2002332196_webqatar13.html"&gt;Qatar Airways picks Airbus A350 over Dreamliner&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Seattle%20Times"&gt;The Seattle Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 13, 2005
