BULLET::::- Bill Curry, Gloria Galloway and Brian Laghi. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20050615.wxvotesb15/BNStory/National/"&gt;Liberals win nervous vote with help from NDP&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABell%20Globemedia%20Inc."&gt;Bell Globemedia Inc.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 15, 2005
BULLET::::- Anne Dawson, Allan Woods and Grant Robertson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.canada.com/national/nationalpost/soundoff/story.html%3Fid%3D259501d2-b13b-403d-9724-79f46bed5299"&gt;Little chance of summer election now&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACanWest%20Global%20Communications%20Corp."&gt;CanWest Global Communications Corp.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 15, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/story/CTVNews/1118847274787_114256474/%3Fhub%3DCanada"&gt;Liberals face another budget showdown Thursday&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABell%20Globemedia%20Inc."&gt;Bell Globemedia Inc.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 15, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2005/WORLD/americas/06/15/canada.politics.ap/index.html"&gt;Canada PM survives Commons votes&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 15

</ul>


