BULLET::::- Joe Bel Bruno. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/news%3Ftmpl%3Dstory%26amp%3Bu%3D/ap/20050618/ap_on_bi_ge/credit_cards_breach"&gt;Security Breach Could Expose 40M to Fraud&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 17,2005

</ul>
