BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//slashdot.org/article.pl%3Fsid%3D05/06/18/2143212"&gt;Coverage at Slashdot&lt;/a&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.corante.com/importance/archives/2005/06/19/la_times_wikitorial_has_left_the_building_for_now.php"&gt;LA Times Wikitorial Has Left the Building (For Now)&lt;/a&gt;
