BULLET::::- Chris Harris. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.mtv.com/news/articles/1504436/20050621/smashing_pumpkins.jhtml%3Fheadlines%3Dtrue"&gt;Billy Corgan Says He Wants To Re-Form Smashing Pumpkins&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMTV"&gt;MTV&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 21, 2005
</ul>
 


