BULLET::::- Associated Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cbsnews.com/stories/2005/06/22/tech/main703485.shtml"&gt;Microchip Pioneer Jack Kilby Dies&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACBS%20News"&gt;CBS News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 22, 2005
BULLET::::- United Press International. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.sciencedaily.com/upi/index.php%3Ffeed%3DScience%26amp%3Barticle%3DUPI-1-20050622-10365700-bc-us-kilby-obit.xml"&gt;Microchip pioneer Jack Kilby dead at 81&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AScience%20Daily"&gt;Science Daily&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 21, 2005
BULLET::::- Spencer Chin. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.eet.com/news/semi/showArticle.jhtml%3FarticleID%3D164901506"&gt;Jack Kilby, co-inventor of the IC, dies at 81&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AEE%20Times"&gt;EE Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 21, 2005
</ul>
 


