BULLET::::- Vladimir Isachenkov. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cleveland.com/news/plaindealer/index.ssf%3F/base/news/1119526309258170.xml%26amp%3Bcoll%3D2"&gt;Solar sail launch failed, vehicle lost, Russia says&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAP"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 23, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//planetary.org/solarsail/latest_update.html"&gt;Solar Sail Latest Updates&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Planetary%20Society"&gt;The Planetary Society&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 22, 2005
