BULLET::::- David Blair. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml%3Fxml%3D/news/2005/06/25/wnig25.xml%26amp%3BsSheet%3D/news/2005/06/25/ixnewstop.html"&gt;£220bn stolen by Nigeria's corrupt rulers&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Daily%20Telegraph"&gt;The Daily Telegraph&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 25, 2005

