BULLET::::- The Economist. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.economist.com/finance/displayStory.cfm%3Fstory_id%3D4079027"&gt;In come the waves&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AEconomist.com"&gt;Economist.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Friday, June 16, 2005

</ul>


