BULLET::::- Michael Vincent. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200506/s1401225.htm"&gt;Australian 'failed' by US military justice&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAustralian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation"&gt;Australian Broadcasting Corporation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 27, 2005

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.news.com.au/story/0%2C10117%2C15744368-1248%2C00.html"&gt;US military justice questioned&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Anews.com.au"&gt;news.com.au&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 27, 2005
</ul>
 


