BULLET::::- The Associated Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20050628/ap_on_re_us/obit_john_walton%3B_ylt%3DAqGCYBEb0eaV5FHN5IrFgfOs0NUE%3B_ylu%3DX3oDMTA3b2NibDltBHNlYwM3MTY-"&gt;Wal-Mart Heir John Walton Dies in Crash&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AYahoo%21%20News"&gt;Yahoo! News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 28, 2005
BULLET::::- Wal-Mart Stores, Inc.. "&lt;a href="http%3A//biz.yahoo.com/prnews/050627/nym213.html%3F.v%3D15"&gt;Philanthropist and Entrepreneur John Walton Killed in Airplane Crash&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AYahoo%21%20Finance"&gt;Yahoo! Finance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 28, 2005
</ul>
 


