BULLET::::- Steve Holland. "&lt;a href="http%3A//today.reuters.co.uk/news/newsArticle.aspx%3Ftype%3DtopNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D2005-06-29T012244Z_01_MCC873992_RTRUKOC_0_IRAQ-USA.xml"&gt;Bush says Iraq war worth it, cites bin Laden&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters.co.uk"&gt;Reuters.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 29, 2005
