<ul>
BULLET::::- Carlotta Gall and David S. Cloud. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/06/29/international/asia/29cnd-copter.html%3Fhp%26amp%3Bex%3D1120104000%26amp%3Ben%3D995e870d866f7eba%26amp%3Bei%3D5094%26amp%3Bpartner%3Dhomepage"&gt;Fighting Prevents U.S. From Learning Fate of 17 on Copter&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANew%20York%20Times"&gt;New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 29, 2005
