BULLET::::- djurban. "&lt;a href="http%3A//7thguard.net/news.php%3Fid%3D4625"&gt;Otwarta wiedza - dwóch pracuje, korzyści dla każdego&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3A7thguard.net"&gt;7thguard.net&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 26, 2005
BULLET::::- Brian Mingus. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.qwikly.com/2005/06/jimmy-wales-announces-wikimedia.html"&gt;Jimmy Wales announces Wikimedia Foundation partnership with KDE&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AQwikly.com"&gt;Qwikly.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 23, 2005
BULLET::::- Sven Krohlas. "&lt;a href="http%3A//dot.kde.org/1119552379/"&gt;KDE and Wikipedia Announce Cooperation&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Adot.KDE"&gt;dot.KDE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 23, 2005

