BULLET::::- Shannon McCaffrey, Knight Ridder. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.bradenton.com/mld/bradenton/news/politics/12027152.htm"&gt;Internet piracy crackdown leads to arrests, works worth $50 million&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHerald%20Today"&gt;Herald Today&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Thu, Jun. 30, 2005
