BULLET::::- Ron Strom. "&lt;a href="http%3A//worldnetdaily.com/news/article.asp%3FARTICLE_ID%3D45029"&gt;Supreme Court Justice faces boot from home?&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWorldNetDaily"&gt;WorldNetDaily&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 28, 2005
BULLET::::- Bob Ellis. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.dakotavoice.com/200506/20050629_1.asp"&gt;Tidal Wave of Support for Souter "Lost Liberty Hotel"&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ADakota%20Voice"&gt;Dakota Voice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 29, 2005
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Associated%20Press"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.boston.com/news/local/new_hampshire/articles/2005/06/29/proposal_replace_souters_home_with_lost_liberty_hotel/"&gt;Proposal: Replace Souter's home with 'Lost Liberty Hotel'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Boston%20Globe"&gt;The Boston Globe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 29, 2005
BULLET::::- Logan Darrow Clements. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.freestarmedia.com/hotellostliberty2.html"&gt;Press Release&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFreestar%20Media%2C%20LLC"&gt;Freestar Media, LLC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 28, 2005

</ul>


