BULLET::::- AP/Reuters. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.rferl.org/featuresarticle/2005/07/4057a4cc-fd4c-42c7-9030-182e88efe9bf.html"&gt;Romania Implements Currency Reform&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ARadio%20Free%20Europe/Radio%20Liberty"&gt;Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 1, 2005
</ul>
 


