BULLET::::- Brian Bakst. "&lt;a href="http%3A//apnews.myway.com//article/20050701/D8B2IERG0.html"&gt;Minn. Government Shuts Down; 9,000 Jobless&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAP"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 1, 2005

</ul>


