BULLET::::- New York Times: &lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/07/02/technology/02soft.html%3Foref%3Dlogin"&gt;Microsoft to Pay I.B.M. $775 Million in Settlement&lt;/a&gt;
