BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp%3Fpage%3Dstory_27-6-2005_pg6_10"&gt;H E A L T H: Scientists find ways to predict and prevent Alzheimer’s&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APakistan%20Daily%20Times"&gt;Pakistan Daily Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 2, 2005
</ul>
 


