BULLET::::- Gulf Times. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.gulf-times.com/site/topics/article.asp%3Fcu_no%3D2%26amp%3Bitem_no%3D42926%26amp%3Bversion%3D1%26amp%3Btemplate_id%3D37%26amp%3Bparent_id%3D17"&gt;Marines murdered my cousin: Iraq UN envoy&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGulf%20Times"&gt;Gulf Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 3, 2005
BULLET::::- Times Staff. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-iraq2jul02%2C1%2C2839087.story%3Fcoll%3Dla-headlines-world%26amp%3Bctrack%3D1%26amp%3Bcset%3Dtrue"&gt;At Least 12 Killed in Suicide Attack on Baghdad Police Station&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ALATimes"&gt;LATimes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 2, 2005

</ul>


