BULLET::::- Chuck Shepard. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.journalnow.com/servlet/Satellite%3Fpagename%3DWSJ%252FMGArticle%252FWSJ_RelishArticle%26amp%3Bc%3DMGArticle%26amp%3Bcid%3D1031783318434%26amp%3Bpath%3D%21entertainment%21general%26amp%3Bs%3D1037645508970"&gt;The litigious society&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUniversal%20Press%20Syndicate"&gt;Universal Press Syndicate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 16, 2005
